data.text: @KashifBoothe I think its a matter of, her being nude etc and controvesial choices about her own life is one thing but actively advertising a product to such an image concious, impressionable audience is dangerous IMO

@KashifBoothe It is not directly encouraging but it could be used as a tool for people who have eating disorders ie this lollipop means I won't eat day...or tomorrow...which could lead to anorexia or continue those who have it
